- Here? Amazing!

889
01:05:09,342 --> 01:05:12,199
She'll turn back and look at you.
Her hair will fly at high speed.

890
01:05:20,122 --> 01:05:21,970
Go, my tiger.
My blessings are with you.

891
01:05:22,050 --> 01:05:23,887
You remember everything, right?
- No.

892
01:05:23,967 --> 01:05:27,221
What? - I forget everything
when I see Piya.

893
01:05:27,301 --> 01:05:28,955
Please come along with me.
- No!

894
01:05:29,483 --> 01:05:32,051
Why?
- Why? What do you mean, why?

895
01:05:32,131 --> 01:05:35,213
Why..why am I asking this question?
Why am I asking this question?

896
01:05:36,864 --> 01:05:38,324
Come on, let's go back home. Please.
- No, no.

897
01:05:38,404 --> 01:05:41,051
Listen, I'll come along with me.

898
01:05:41,131 --> 01:05:42,706
I'll be near you,
but I won't be with you.

899
01:05:42,786 --> 01:05:43,846
All right?
- Okay.

