01:06:23,426 --> 01:06:24,718
Action!

908
01:06:24,798 --> 01:06:26,631
Hello! Yes, everything is fine.

909
01:06:27,188 --> 01:06:29,051
Oh! Piya!

910
01:06:29,131 --> 01:06:31,465
Cut! Cut! Cut!
What are you doing? Go back.

911
01:06:31,548 --> 01:06:34,190
Energy. Loud. Feeling. Emotion.

912
01:06:34,929 --> 01:06:37,173
Take 2. Ready? Action!

913
01:06:37,621 --> 01:06:40,100
Yes! No, no,
the weather is absolutely..

914
01:06:41,667 --> 01:06:43,663
Oh! Piya?

915
01:06:44,430 --> 01:06:45,756
Cut! Cut!

916
01:06:45,962 --> 01:06:47,840
What are you doing? Go back.

917
01:06:48,953 --> 01:06:50,511
