918
01:06:50,591 --> 01:06:52,340
Take 3. Action!

919
01:06:52,423 --> 01:06:53,840
Yes, everything I fine..yes..

920
01:06:53,923 --> 01:06:55,798
Piya!

921
01:07:39,465 --> 01:07:40,756
Hello?

922
01:07:43,881 --> 01:07:45,131
Hi!

923
01:07:50,256 --> 01:07:52,506
