930
01:08:45,314 --> 01:08:47,010
Darn kids!

931
01:08:51,131 --> 01:08:52,631
Nice meeting you.

932
01:08:52,715 --> 01:08:54,256
Hi Piya.
- Hi. - Okay. Nice meeting you.

933
01:08:54,336 --> 01:08:55,840
Hi. Hi.

934
