946
01:09:29,587 --> 01:09:31,464
I have a bright idea.

947
01:09:32,225 --> 01:09:34,714
Sorry, I was listening to you both.
I couldn't help myself.

948
01:09:35,163 --> 01:09:38,259
This is a micro walkie-talkie.

949
01:09:38,340 --> 01:09:43,173
